BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART:20090709T230000Z
DTEND:20090710T020000Z
DTSTAMP:20260315T222701Z
UID:nhi5126tkdkhvbbg76dikigt1c@google.com
CREATED:20090723T055400Z
DESCRIPTION:This will be the first workshop held by Baltimore Node\, a newl
 y formed hackerspace currently looking for a home. The workshop will center
  around the building of an ambient orb clone (http://www.ambientdevices.com
 /cat/orb/orborder.html) using a high powered LED to display data passed to 
 an Arduino (http://www.Arduino.cc/en/Guide/Introduction).\n\nThe workshop w
 ill include some light soldering but people will be on hand to offer help t
 o those that need it.\n\nUPDATE: Notes and code available from the workshop
  available here: http://wiki.baltimorenode.org/index.php?title=Workshop1
LAST-MODIFIED:20230110T145026Z
LOCATION:113 W North Ave\, Baltimore MD
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Workshop1 "Ambient Orb"
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
