DTEND:20090919T200000Z
DTSTAMP:20260315T222701Z
UID:0g2e9vh5t7aqtp15q77g3smsv0@google.com
CLASS:PUBLIC
CREATED:20090828T041532Z
DESCRIPTION:Pedal Hacking Workshop\n\nBaltimore Node\n120 W North Ave\nBalt
 imore MD 21201\n\nSeptember 19\, 2009\n1pm - 4pm\n\n$15 for non-members\n\n
 The Pedal Hacking Workshop is Baltimore Node's first event at our new space
  in The Load of Fun Building on 120 W. North Ave\, Baltimore. Bring your gu
 itar pedals and parts to work and learn in an open workshop environment. Ba
 ltimore Node is supplying the workspace\, some basic tools\, and soldering 
 instruction.\n\nExamples of projects being worked on during the workshop:\n
     * Boss BD2 Mod\n    * Tube Screamer TS808 build\n    * Repairing pedals
 \n\nAttendance to the workshop is free for Baltimore Node members\, and $15
  for non-members. Please register via Eventbrite to reserve a seat.\n    ht
 tp://www.eventbrite.com/event/416665257\n\nFor more information and members
 hip details:\n    http://baltimorenode.org\n    http://wiki.baltimorenode.o
 rg/index.php?title=Pedal_Hacking_Workshop
LAST-MODIFIED:20230110T144806Z
LOCATION:120 W North Ave Baltimore MD 21201
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Pedal Hacking Workshop
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
