CREATED:20240829T181139Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Lyssandra Allen\, an Intelligence Analyst at the FBI Baltimo
 re Field Office\, has conducted some research and discovered some misunders
 tandings about 3D printing and firearms\, and have developed a short presen
 tation to help spread awareness on these topics. <br><br>She's presenting t
 his 20 minute presentation at the Baltimore Node Makerspace during Open Hac
 k at 8pm.<br><br></p><ul><li>Member Forum Thread: <a href="https://forum.ba
 ltimorenode.org/t/fbi-presentarion-sept-19-8pm/6694"><u>https://forum.balti
 morenode.org/t/fbi-presentarion-sept-19-8pm/6694</u></a></li></ul><ul><li>O
 fficers / Organizing Thread: <a href="https://forum.baltimorenode.org/t/fol
 low-up-regarding-3d-printing-capabilities/6675" target="_blank">https://for
 um.baltimorenode.org/t/follow-up-regarding-3d-printing-capabilities/6675</a
 ><br></li><br></ul><p></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240829T181427Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:🗨️ FBI 3D Printing Awareness Presentation
TRANSP:OPAQUE
