UID:d8lf9ahj68pjvr493pme0amcl8@google.com
CREATED:20100110T171436Z
DESCRIPTION:Do you see something that can be made more glamorous with built
  in\nLED lights? Do you have something that you put LEDs on that you want\n
 to blink in a smart way? Tired of that bundle of wires on your project\nalw
 ays falling apart? Wouldn't it be cool if your pants made music?\nBaltimore
  Node wants to help.\n\nBaltimore Node is a hacker space. We have gathered 
 our tools and\ncreated a space for building projects in a social and collab
 orative\nenvironment. 1st and 3rd Wednesdays at 7:30pm Baltimore Node will 
 be\nopening up to share our tools and expertise with you and your ideas.\nN
 ode Members will be on hand to offer guidance on how to get from the\niniti
 al thought to materials\, setup and assembly to finish your\nproject.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230110T145022Z
LOCATION:120 W. North Ave. Balitmore\, MD
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Colab Wednesdays (On Hold)
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
