DTSTAMP:20260315T222701Z
UID:hs6vs09d9s6urt4orothtem4cc@google.com
CREATED:20100110T170917Z
DESCRIPTION:Do you see something that can be made more glamourous with buil
 t in\nLED lights? Do you have something that you put LEDs on that you want\
 nto blink in a smart way? Tired of that bundle of wires on your project\nal
 ways falling apart? Wouldn't it be cool if your pants made music?\nBaltimor
 e Node wants to help.\n\nBaltimore Node is a hacker space. We have gathered
  our tools and\ncreated a space for building projects in a social and colla
 borative\nenvironment. 1st and 3rd Wednesdays at 7:30pm Baltimore Node will
  be\nopening up to share our tools and expertise with you and your ideas.\n
 Node Members will be on hand to offer guidance on how to get from the\ninit
 ial thought to materials\, setup and assembly to finish your\nproject.
LAST-MODIFIED:20230110T144709Z
LOCATION:120 W. North Ave. Baltimore\, MD
SEQUENCE:3
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Colab Wednesdays (On Hold)
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
