CREATED:20181026T013119Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Baltimore’s Node’s 9th Birthday Party! \n\n Our
  nine years of making\, collaborating\, ideas\, and connections will be cel
 ebrated in true maker fashion\, working together on a group build to assemb
 le a 9 foot tall sculpture.  The piece was designed by George Hart and is m
 ade of 193 3D printed pieces that were crowd-sourced from all over the worl
 d\, plus 416 wooden dowel rods\, those don’t seem quite as exciting\, but a
 re apparently important.    \n\nWe would love to join us if you were a memb
 er in the past\, someone who is thinking about joining\, just want to check
  the space out\, if you are interested in maker spaces\, building projects\
 , electronics\, art\, programming\, building\, crafting\, or having a space
  to think through big ideas (or if just want to party).  Everyone is welcom
 e.  We will have some food to share and you are welcome to contribute some 
 if you would like.
LAST-MODIFIED:20181026T013119Z
LOCATION:Baltimore Node Hackerspace\, 2106 N Lovegrove St\, Baltimore\, MD 
 21218\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Baltimore Node Turns 9 - 9' Sculpture Build and Birthday Party!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
