DESCRIPTION:We are hoping as many members as possible will be able to make 
 it to the Node for the spring clean.  On this day we will be going through 
 stuff in the space to determine what to keep and what we can give away (we 
 have too much stuff) as well as doing some cleaning and organizing.  The ul
 timate goal is to have a more functional space.  I think I overhead someone
  mention something about pizza.  
