BEGIN:VEVENT
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20240725T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20240725T220000
DTSTAMP:20260315T222701Z
UID:2bgkqe6ar0dppv3cfr64rbrjft@google.com
RECURRENCE-ID;TZID=America/New_York:20240725T190000
CREATED:20220610T003207Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>We're hijacking our weekly open hack night for our anniversa
 ry party! Come hang with Node members and others in the community and enjoy
  some food\, conversation\, and a tour of our space! We've got a woodshop\,
  metal shop\, laser cutters\, a CNC router\, 3d printers\, electronics\, an
 d a whole lot more!</p><p>If you are interested in learning more about our 
 Makerspace\; you are invited to join us for an informal evening where you c
 an get a tour of the place and meet some of our members. Find out how to be
 come involved. Come to share ideas and projects.</p><p>For those concerned 
 or not able to join us in person we still have an online presence at <a hre
 f="https://meet.baltimorenode.org/OpenHack" target="_blank">https://meet.ba
 ltimorenode.org/OpenHack</a> for a virtual evening.</p><p>You yes you can b
 ecome a member of the Node and get full 24/7 access to an amazing shop and 
